headline: 4 Healthcare Stocks Rising More Than 50% in 2024 With Room to Grow
summary: Medical stocks are expected to reap the benefits of affordable health insurance plans, rising surgeries and widespread adoption of telehealth services in the days ahead. However, inflation and supply-chain woes may act as spoilsport.
